there's the envelope.

34
00:02:50,003 --> 00:02:51,003
-Uh, what do you mean?

35
00:02:54,003 --> 00:02:55,970
L: He's holding what looks
like an envelope when

36
00:02:56,003 --> 00:02:58,336
he passes through
the ticket gate.

37
00:02:58,370 --> 00:02:59,203
-You're right!

38
00:02:59,236 --> 00:03:00,870
It's there, under his arm.

39
00:03:00,903 --> 00:03:04,670
But in the footage right
before his death, it's gone.

40
00:03:04,703 --> 00:03:07,370
I can't believe you
actually caught that.

41
00:03:07,403 --> 00:03:09,470
-Well, I don't see an
envelope on this list

42
00:03:09,503 --> 00:03:11,203
of his personal effects.

43
