L: Which means it was
left on the train.

44
00:03:13,970 --> 00:03:18,103
And if you watch closely
at the very end here,

45
00:03:18,136 --> 00:03:20,603
it seems like he's straining
to look inside the train

46
00:03:20,636 --> 00:03:21,570
before the doors close.

47
00:03:21,603 --> 00:03:23,070
You can see right here.

48
00:03:23,103 --> 00:03:25,470
-If that's the case, do you
think it could mean something?

49
00:03:25,503 --> 00:03:28,503
-Wouldn't it be interesting
if Kira was on that train.

50
00:03:28,536 --> 00:03:29,703
-That's impossible.

51
00:03:29,736 --> 00:03:32,970
-I admit, I find it hard
to believe, as well.

52
00:03:33,003 --> 00:03:34,370
There's no reason
for Kira to come

53
00:03:34,403 --> 00:03:35,803
to the scene of
his own crime when

54
00:03:35,836 --> 00:03:37,570
