55
00:03:37,603 --> 00:03:41,636
Well, maybe he was counting
on us to make that assumption

56
00:03:41,670 --> 00:03:45,536
and figured he could get
away with such a bold move.

57
00:03:45,570 --> 00:03:46,036
Mmm.

58
00:03:48,870 --> 00:03:49,370
-Mmm.

59
00:03:52,303 --> 00:03:54,303
RYUK: What's going
on with you, Light?

60
00:03:54,336 --> 00:03:56,803
You haven't stopped writing
criminals' names in the death

61
00:03:56,836 --> 00:03:58,236
note for four days straight.

62
00:03:58,270 --> 00:03:59,970
