63
00:04:00,003 --> 00:04:03,036
I don't see the point in writing
these names weeks in advance.

64
00:04:03,070 --> 00:04:05,236
I've never seen the death
note used like this.

65
00:04:05,270 --> 00:04:06,736
-Consider it insurance.

66
00:04:06,770 --> 00:04:09,736
