68
00:04:10,903 --> 00:04:13,003
If criminals stopped
dying at the same time,

69
00:04:13,036 --> 00:04:15,070
it wouldn't be difficult
to connect the two.

70
00:04:15,103 --> 00:04:16,836
-So that's what this is.

71
00:04:16,870 --> 00:04:18,470
