76
00:04:26,670 --> 00:04:29,803
But I suppose any time before
the end of their lifespan

77
00:04:29,836 --> 00:04:31,070
should work.

78
00:04:31,103 --> 00:04:33,103
-I really can't
count on you, can I?

79
00:04:33,136 --> 00:04:34,903
-You got that right.

80
