to turn on your cell phone now.

91
00:04:57,136 --> 00:04:58,836
Actually, please turn
it on right away.

92
00:04:58,870 --> 00:04:59,970
-Uh, sure.

93
00:05:04,303 --> 00:05:07,036
-Yes, this is Suzuki, head of
Kira's investigation public

94
00:05:07,070 --> 00:05:09,370
information division.

95
00:05:09,403 --> 00:05:11,770
Raye Penber's fiancee?

96
00:05:11,803 --> 00:05:14,136
Naomi Misora.

97
00:05:14,170 --> 00:05:15,603
I've heard that name before.

98
00:05:18,903 --> 00:05:20,836
So it's her.

99
00:05:20,870 --> 00:05:22,936
She's from the Los
Angeles BB Murder Case.

100
00:05:22,970 --> 00:05:24,336
That's right.

101
00:05:24,370 --> 00:05:26,170
She was working under me.

102
00:05:26,203 --> 00:05:28,670
I guess she must have come
to Japan with her fiance.

103
00:05:33,703 --> 00:05:35,870
Well, apparently she's
been missing since the day

104
00:05:35,903 --> 00:05:37,670
after her fiance died.

105
00:05:37,703 --> 00:05:39,236
